OL,3,CChairman apologises for 'error of
OL,4,Cjudgment' over editing of Donald Trump
OL,5,Cspeech
OL,7,FBBC Chairman, Samir Shah has said the
OL,8,Fcorporation accepted that the way a
OL,9,Fspeech by Donald Trump had been edited
OL,10,Ffor a Panorama documentary had given
OL,11,F"the impression of a direct call for
OL,12,Fviolent action."
OL,14,FBBC chairman Samir Shah has apologised
OL,15,Ffor an "error of judgment" over the
OL,16,Fediting of a speech by Donald Trump,
OL,17,Fwhich has led to the resignation of
OL,18,Ftwo senior BBC executives.
