OL,3,CChairman apologises for 'error of
OL,4,Cjudgment' over editing of Donald Trump
OL,5,Cspeech
OL,7,FIn a letter to the Culture, Media and
OL,8,FSport Committee, Mr Shah said the
OL,9,Fcorporation accepted that the way the
OL,10,Fspeech had been edited for a Panorama
OL,11,Fdocumentary had given "the impression
OL,12,Fof a direct call for violent action."
OL,14,FThe BBC said it has received
OL,15,Fcommunication from Trump over the
OL,16,Fediting of the documentary, broadcast
OL,17,Fthe week before last year's US
OL,18,Felection, but did not confirm the US
OL,19,Fpresident has threatened to sue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
