OL,5,Cspeech
OL,7,FHe said: "We are now considering how
OL,8,Fto reply to him."
OL,10,FAsked directly if Trump has said he
OL,11,Fwill be suing the BBC, Mr Shah told
OL,12,FBBC News: "I do not know that yet, but
OL,13,Fhe's a litigious fellow so we should
OL,14,Fbe prepared for all outcomes."
OL,16,FBBC News CEO Deborah Turness and BBC
OL,17,Fdirector-general Tim Davie resigned
OL,18,Ffollowing the criticism.
