OL,5,Cspeech
OL,7,FTheir resignation follows the release
OL,8,Fof a memo by Michael Prescott, a
OL,9,Fformer external adviser to the BBC's
OL,10,Feditorial standards committee, which
OL,11,Fraised concerns in the summer about
OL,12,Fthe way President Trump's speech on
OL,13,FJanuary 6, 2021, had been edited.
OL,15,FClips were spliced together in the
OL,16,Fdocumentary 'Trump: A Second Chance?'
OL,17,Fto make it appear he had told
OL,18,Fsupporters he was going to walk to the
OL,19,FUS Capitol with them to "fight like
OL,20,Fhell".
