OL,7,FDeborah Turness spoke to reporters
OL,8,Foutside Broadcasting House on Monday
OL,9,Fmorning following her resignation over
OL,10,Fthe weekend.
OL,12,FIn his letter, Mr Shah said there have
OL,13,Fbeen more than 500 complaints since
OL,14,Fthe publication of the memo, and that
OL,15,Fit is "simply not true" that Mr
OL,16,FPrescott "uncovered" issues that the
OL,17,FBBC has sought to "bury".
