OL,7,FOn the editing of the clip, Mr Shah
OL,8,Fsaid the BBC's editorial guidelines
OL,9,Fand standards committee was told by
OL,10,FBBC News the purpose of doing so was
OL,11,F"to convey the message of the speech
OL,12,Fmade by President Trump so that
OL,13,FPanorama's audience could better
OL,14,Funderstand how it had been received by
OL,15,FPresident Trump's supporters and what
OL,16,Fwas happening on the ground at that
OL,17,Ftime."
