OL,7,FHe said the issue was discussed as
OL,8,Fpart of a wider review of the BBC's US
OL,9,Felection coverage, but was not pursued
OL,10,Ffurther at that time as it had not
OL,11,Fattracted significant audience
OL,12,Ffeedback.
OL,14,FThe letter continued: "The points
OL,15,Fraised in the review were relayed to
OL,16,Fthe Panorama team, including the
OL,17,Fdecision-making on this edit. With
OL,18,Fhindsight, it would have been better
OL,19,Fto take more formal action."
