OL,7,FDowning Street has said the BBC is not
OL,8,Fcorrupt or institutionally biased
OL,9,Fafter hitting back at claims made by
OL,10,FPresident Trump and other critics of
OL,11,Fthe public broadcaster.
OL,13,FA spokesman for the prime minister
OL,14,Fsaid: "On the question of is the BBC
OL,15,Fcorrupt? No.
OL,17,F"The BBC has a vital role in an age of
OL,18,Fdisinformation... where there's a
OL,19,Fclear argument for a robust, impartial
OL,20,FBritish news service to deliver, and
OL,21,Fthat case is stronger than ever."
