OL,7,FSpeaking to reporters outside
OL,8,FBroadcasting House, Ms Turness said:
OL,9,F"I stepped down over the weekend
OL,10,Fbecause the buck stops with me, but I
OL,11,Fwould like to make one thing very
OL,12,Fclear.
OL,14,F"BBC News is not institutionally
OL,15,Fbiased, that's why it's the world's
OL,16,Fmost trusted news provider."
