OL,7,FAsked why mistakes were not dealt
OL,8,Fwith, including on Trump, on
OL,9,Fantisemitism, and on women's rights,
OL,10,FMs Turness replied: "I'm sure that
OL,11,Fstory will emerge."
OL,13,FMr Davie said his departure from the
OL,14,Fcorporation would not be immediate and
OL,15,Fhe is "working through" timings to
OL,16,Fensure an "orderly transition" over
OL,17,Fthe coming months.
